As the overall height distribution reduces due to the fabrication of
large semi- spherical NPs, the FFT spectra also show the round pattern and contract
in size. In addition, the surface morphologies were investigated and quantified by
the surface parameters in terms of RMS roughness (Rq) and surface area ratio (SAR). Here, the Rq provides the average of surface profile height (yi) as Eq. 3,3Rq=1n∑i=1nyi2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
